            . I am an officer. I stopped the prisoner - Marshall was pursuing him; these are the ribbons.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went for three-quarters of a yard of shoe ribbon - the boy came in after me; the witness said, "Have you taken any ribbon" - he said, No; he ran out and dropped the ribbon at my feet.</p>
